body:
I see.  That seems to be a bug caused by a difference of compile options.  "inception_dummy_int_data_224x224" is a dummy input data which can be arbitrary binary.  So if you just want to pass the build, please try just putting
`uint8_t inception_dummy_int_data_224x224[224*224*3] = {};
in tensorflow/contrib/hvx/hexagon_controller/src_dummy_data/inception_v3_dummy_int_data.c

Let me know the compile result.
